.TH "set_rx_intr_params" 9 "set_rx_intr_params" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
set_rx_intr_params \- set a net devices's RX interrupt holdoff paramete!
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" set_rx_intr_params
.BI "(struct net_device *dev "  ","
.BI "unsigned int us "  ","
.BI "unsigned int cnt "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
the network device
.IP "us" 12
the hold-off time in us, or 0 to disable timer
.IP "cnt" 12
the hold-off packet count, or 0 to disable counter
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Set the RX interrupt hold-off parameters for a network device.
